{"tid":1823168,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網傳解僱全部散工　美心：不評論市場傳聞","createTime":"2020-01-13T12:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T12:46:05.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5f016a34ba8eb551a48c8c5842066e6066bb70d9","tid":1823168,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T12:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/maxim-11_83Uaa_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fmaxim-11_83Uaa_1200x0.png&h=373880a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上有 facebook 專頁引述消息指，美心昨日起裁減所有長期散工，並引述知情人士透露，銷量受到大減，「生產多於銷售」，故裁員節省開支。美心回覆《立場新聞》查詢時稱，不評論市場傳聞。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook 專頁「家明」昨晚表示收到獨家消息，指美心西餅廠房昨日開始裁減所有長期散工。該帖稱，美心節省開支多時，僅僱用少量長工，並依靠長期散工維持日常運作。是次裁員意味著，「分店銷量受到重大影響，生產多於銷售」，需要縮減人手節省開支。<br />\n<br />\n美心集團創辦人伍沾德長女伍淑清，多次發表反對示威的言論，引起示威者不滿，集團旗下商店遂成破壞目標。「家明」專頁帖子又稱，「反送中」引發的社會運動以來，美心旗下受影響的商店一度多達71間，目前亦有至少有10多間分店無限期停業。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E8%A7%A3%E5%83%B1%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E6%95%A3%E5%B7%A5-%E7%BE%8E%E5%BF%83-%E4%B8%8D%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%82%B3%E8%81%9E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%2583%25B1%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%2595%25A3%25E5%25B7%25A5-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%2581%259E%2F&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHCWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=c383af84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%2583%25B1%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%2595%25A3%25E5%25B7%25A5-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%2581%259E%2F&h=887e5b34\" data-